content:
Vlocity OmniAnalytics can track user interactions with OmniScripts and FlexCards in combination with Google Analytics and Google Tag Manager.

Vlocity OmniAnalytics integrates with Google Universal Analytics. It doesn't integrate with Google Analytics 4.

To configure OmniAnalytics to work with an analytics vendor other than Google Analytics, see Workflow for Configuring OmniAnalytics for a Third-Party Analytics Vendor.

An example OmniScript illustrates a simplified purchasing process for one of several smartphones and a FlexCard that redirects the user to the Google website.

Complete the workflow to:

* Configure Internal OmniAnalytics
* Set up Google Analytics and Google Tag Manager
* Add ecommerce data to the example OmniScript and Card
* Create a tracking configuration and add event types
* Edit the Vlocity Tracking Group for Google Analytics

Test the tracking by interacting with the example OmniScript and Card, then view the tracking data in Google Analytics.
title: Configuring OmniAnalytics with Google Analytics
